room_title: Escape room "The Toy Box" by ZScape Games in Livermore
room_address: 2110 Omega Rd Suite E, San Ramon, CA 94583
room_description:
Shrunken down to the size of a footstool, you've found yourself in a magical small-scale adventure. One minor detail, you never finished building your grow machine!
Use the surrounding objects in clever ways to solve puzzles and find clues to build your device and ultimately escape The Toy Box before your parents return!
